                    Company Description








Truly smart for future. Truly - Forbes 2016 Asia's Fab 50 Companies, was founded in 1978 and the headquarters is located in HK while the factories are in Shanwei and Huizhou City of Guangdong with the total area of 1,500,000+㎡, listed in Hong Kong Stock Exchange in 1991 (00732.HK). Truly has concentrated on developing, manufacturing and marketing one-stop solution of display, touch panel, optical bonding, compact camera module, fingerprint identification and glass cover which has been widely applied to automotive, industrial, medical, IoT, wearable and smartphone applications.智慧信利，同心致远。








