Truly International posts qtrly net profit of HK$223 million<0732.HK>
Wednesday, 18 May 2016 04:44am EDT 
Truly International Holdings Ltd <0732.HK>: Board resolved to pay an interim quarterly dividend of 2 hk cents per share for the three months ended 31 March 2016 . Unaudited consolidated revenue for three months ended 31 March 2016 was approximately hk$4.69 billion, up 0.5% . Net profit for three months period from 1 January 2016 to 31 March 2016 hk$223 million, about 12.9 percent more than corresponding period in 2015 . 
			
